wlDescription: Try these BEGINNER level workouts if you are new to exercising or need to ease back into it.
Perform these INTERMEDIATE workouts with solid technique before moving on to higher levels.
Some of these ADVANCED workouts may be harder than they appear.
These workouts are definitely challenging and are considered EXPERT level.
Attempt these workouts if you are a MASTER of calisthenics and enjoy an extremely tough challenge.
